<h2>Industrial Automation &amp; Robotics Technology</h2>
<h3>Career Opportunities</h3>
<p>As more firms introduce automated production equipment, workers will be needed to ensure that machines are properly maintained and consistently in operation. This program will prepare the student for entry-level as an Industrial Maintenance Technician, Industrial Machinery Repairer, Industrial Maintenance Mechanic, Industrial Field Engineer, or an Electrical/Electronics Installer or Repairer.</p>
